        <section id="cleansing">
            <h2>Cleansing</h2>
            <p>Start your skincare routine by cleansing your face with a gentle cleanser to remove dirt and makeup.
Cleansing with essential products is important because it helps remove dirt, impurities, and excess oils from the skin, promoting a clear, healthy complexion. 
It also enhances the effectiveness of subsequent skincare treatments and allows the skin to breathe and regenerate properly. 
Essential cleansing products maintain the skin's natural balance, preventing irritation and maintaining hydration.
</p>
            <img src="https://i1.wp.com/wakeupformakeup.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/best-gentle-cleansers.jpg"width="150";height="150" alt="Cleansing image">
            <p>Recommended product: <a href="https://www.sephora.com//cleanser" target="_blank">Gentle Face Cleanser</a></p>
        </section>

        <section id="moisturizing">
            <h2>Moisturizing</h2>
            <p>Keep your skin hydrated by using a moisturizer suitable for your skin type.
Using a moisturizer with essential products is crucial for maintaining skin hydration, preventing dryness, and restoring the skin's natural barrier. 
It helps lock in moisture, supports skin elasticity, and protects against environmental stressors. 
Regular moisturizing with quality products keeps the skin smooth, healthy, and balanced, reducing the risk of irritation and premature aging.</p>
            <img src="Kosmetyki Mary Kay.jpg"width="150";height="150 alt="Moisturizing image">
            <p>Recommended product: <a href="https://www.kiehls.com//moisturizer" target="_blank">Hydrating Moisturizer</a></p>
        </section>

        <section id="sunscreen">
            <h2>Sunscreen</h2>
            <p>Protect your skin from harmful UV rays by applying sunscreen with at least SPF 30.
Using sunscreen with essential ingredients is vital for protecting the skin from harmful UV rays, which can cause premature aging, sunburn, and increase the risk of skin cancer. 
It helps prevent damage to the skin's collagen and elastin, maintaining skin health and preventing pigmentation. 
Regular use of sunscreen keeps the skin safe and youthful by shielding it from both UVA and UVB rays, making it an essential part of any skincare routine.</p>
            <img src="https://imgmedia.lbb.in/media/2023/06/647867cc3d39531e62c51e2c_1685612492070.jpg"width="150";height="150" alt="Sunscreen image">
            <p>Recommended product: <a href="https://www.cerave.com//sunscreen" target="_blank">SPF 30+ Sunscreen</a></p>
        </section>

